Lihat. 8 Juni.

275
00:22:02,079 --> 00:22:03,480
Tepat sebelum dia hilang.

276
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,000
Kau membohongiku?

277
00:22:08,119 --> 00:22:09,319
Dasar bajingan.

278
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,680
Tidak! Astaga.

279
00:22:10,759 --> 00:22:13,519
Aku tak menjawab sebab aku berada
di acara peringatan teman.

280
00:22:13,599 --> 00:22:14,440
Kembalikan itu.

281
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:17,799
Nanti, tapi pertama, masuk ke truk.

282
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:18,880
Truk apa?

283
