Johannes ada di dalam.

284
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,200
Pria Finlandia.

285
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:25,480
Apa-apaan ini?

286
00:22:26,319 --> 00:22:27,759
Dan saudara, Dragos.

287
00:22:28,599 --> 00:22:30,000
Dan ayah, Florin.

288
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:33,440
Apa kabar, Pak Florin?

289
00:22:41,359 --> 00:22:42,559
Apa kabar, Marcus?

290
00:22:47,519 --> 00:22:50,279
Kami menunggumu kemarin, Marcus,
tapi kau tak datang.

291
