00:26:22,799 --> 00:26:23,640
Apa?

353
00:26:24,359 --> 00:26:25,279
Tolong aku.

354
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,200
Pegang tangannya.

355
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:29,960
